service

public Ra service(String serviceName)
Stablished the current service to invoke. From this point, all the set and header calls are applied to this service. If you need to call another service, execute this method again with the new service. This will remove all the values established, and the new service will contain the values setup in the configuration file

Parameters:
serviceName - name of the service to load. It will throw a runtime error if service is not in the current config.
Returns:
the same Ra object.
